      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p>A rogue spirit is drawn to you—perhaps it’s a past victim? Acquire the services of a Whisper or Rail Jack to attempt to destroy or banish it, or deal with it yourself.</p>\n<p><em>They can hire an NPC by using the acquire asset downtime activity (see page </em><em>153). Roll the NPC’s quality level as a fortune roll to see how well they deal </em><em>with the spirit.</em></p>"
